I will implement the data deletion feature with a complete audit history and stock restoration logic.

**Key Features:**
1.  **Deletion Capability**: Admins will see a "Delete" (Trash) button on every row in the Daily Costing Report on the Dashboard.
2.  **Stock Restoration**: When an entry is deleted, the system will automatically **add back** the consumed ingredients to the Inventory to ensure stock levels remain accurate.
3.  **Deletion History**: A new "Deletion History" tab will be added to the Sidebar (Admin only) to track exactly when and what was deleted.

Here are the changes:

# Updated files:

## types.ts

Added `DeletionLog` interface to track deleted entry details.

